  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dc0 \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0db8\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kamal Gunaratne to Human Rights Commission",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Human Rights Commission has inquired from the Defense Secretary General (retired) Kamal Gunaratne regarding the recent incident of an army officer kicking a person at the Yakgahapitiya petrol station in Kurunegala.",
        "The Secretary of Defense appeared there yesterday (5th) according to a notice given by the Chairperson of the Human Rights Commission.",
        "The Defense Secretary has informed the Commission that he condemns this incident as the Defense Secretary and that the Army has started an investigation in this regard."
      ],
